data.description: Welcome home! Come by and check out this 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bath home located in Teas Lake! The home is located on a cul-de-sac and No Back Neighbors! As you walk in the home you will find high ceilings and a newly painted dining room just off the entry. The galley style kitchen has tons of countertop space, beautiful cabinets, a built in desk and stainless steel appliances have recently been replaced!! The living room has a wall of windows overlooking the huge deck and beautiful backyard. As you head upstairs you will find 3 bedrooms, 2 baths and a gameroom. You will enjoy this very large primary bedroom! There is an ensuite primary bath with a soaking tub, separate shower and vanity with double sinks. Just wait until you see this large deck overlooking the tranquil, peaceful backyard. You will easily imagine yourself enjoying coffee in the morning out there or entertaining a big get together for family party's! Willis ISD. Call for an appointment!
